      • step

        public boolean step()
             throws NoRouteFoundException
        Takes a step through the maze. Multiple uses of the method will either solve the maze or throw a NoRouteFoundException.
        Returns:
        Returns true if the maze has been solved, returns false otherwise
        Throws:
